{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/work/relic-scout/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Relic Scout","date":"2017-04-19T00:00:00.000Z","date_pretty":"April 19th, 2017","date_from_now":"3 years ago","last_modified_at":"2019-12-10T21:51:32.000Z","last_modified_at_from_now":"4 months ago","path":"/work/relic-scout/","author":null,"excerpt":"Site design and creative for Relic Scout — an app to make collecting simpler, while saving you money.","tags":["design","web development"],"image":null,"toc":null,"comments":false,"comments_locked":null,"hide_meta":true},"id":"ce27e7fd-1452-5b1d-af26-0ee0c6174d2b","html":"<p>Eko Wave, a company started by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/endonend\">two</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/bjpmba\">pals</a> and myself, just took the wraps off our first app — <strong>Relic Scout</strong>. Last week we launched a teaser site and couldn’t be prouder of the work that we’ve done so far.</p>\n<p>I had a lot of fun creating the 8bit pixel art and applying a parallax effect to it using the <a href=\"https://github.com/cameronmcefee/plax\">jQuery plugin Plax</a>. If you collect sports cards, magic cards, coins, or comics, you should check it out.</p>\n<p><img src=\"../../images/relic-scout-browser-750.jpg\" alt=\"Relic Scout homepage screenshot\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"style-tiles\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#style-tiles\" aria-label=\"style tiles permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Style tiles</h2>\